Package: handcalcs
Title: Generate Hand-calculated Solutions for Statistics Problems
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Travis", "Carter", , "tjcarter@roanoke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4499-7300"))
Description: Used to develop practice problems for statistics courses. For a variety of different basic statistical operations (e.g., for use in an introductory stats course), generate data and nicely formatted step-by-step solutions.
